<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1947-07-31T19:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1947-07-31T19:00:00-05:00" n="804" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d804">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">501.BC/7–3147: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the <gloss type="to">Embassy in India</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#left">
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">confidential</hi>
                                <lb/>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">u.s. urgent</hi>
                                <lb/>
                                <gloss target="#t_Niact1">
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">niact</hi>
                                </gloss>
                            </seg>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1947-07-31T20:00:00-04:00">July 31,
                                    1947—8 p.m.</date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>460. You may inform Nehru US Govt has noted India’s letter to UN Security
                            Council. US is urgently considering what measures might most
                            appropriately be taken to bring about cessation of hostilities and
                            resumption of negotiations looking toward a peaceful settlement Dutch
                            and Indonesian differences.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Marshall</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>